37533/2244e/657c96e6c9f63aebd20ad1f26fe611a8.jpg 400w,\n/static/56a8ed2fe8cc230d3321b30aba837533/14b42/657c96e6c9f63aebd20ad1f26fe611a8.jpg 800w,\n/static/56a8ed2fe8cc230d3321b30aba837533/47498/657c96e6c9f63aebd20ad1f26fe611a8.jpg 1200w,\n/static/56a8ed2fe8cc230d3321b30aba837533/ec6c5/657c96e6c9f63aebd20ad1f26fe611a8.jpg 1280w","srcWebp":"/static/56a8ed2fe8cc230d3321b30aba837533/58556/657c96e6c9f63aebd20ad1f26fe611a8.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/56a8ed2fe8cc230d3321b30aba837533/61e93/657c96e6c9f63aebd20ad1f26fe611a8.webp 200w,\n/static/56a8ed2fe8cc230d3321b30aba837533/1f5c5/657c96e6c9f63aebd20ad1f26fe611a8.webp 400w,\n/static/56a8ed2fe8cc230d3321b30aba837533/58556/657c96e6c9f63aebd20ad1f26fe611a8.webp 800w,\n/static/56a8ed2fe8cc230d3321b30aba837533/99238/657c96e6c9f63aebd20ad1f26fe611a8.webp 1200w,\n/static/56a8ed2fe8cc230d3321b30aba837533/135cd/657c96e6c9f63aebd20ad1f26fe611a8.webp 1280w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}},"title":"MXC in Brussels, Amsterdam, Seoul, and Barcelona","post":{"content":"## MXC in Brussels, Amsterdam, Seoul, and Barcelona\nThe MXC team is getting busy traveling! Sheen is back from EIT Digital Conference in Brussels. MXC hosted its annual Amsterdam meet up, and you can meet MXC in Seoul and Barcelona.\nThis is the original script of the MXC News Update.\n\n\n## MXC in Brussels, Amsterdam, Seoul, and Barcelona\nThe MXC team is getting busy traveling! Sheen is back from EIT Digital Conference in Brussels. MXC hosted its annual Amsterdam meet up, and you can meet MXC in Seoul and Barcelona.\nThis is the original script of the MXC News Update.\n\nMXC in Brussels, MXC in Berlin and MXC in Amsterdam. Where are we going next? You’ll find out in this week’s news update!\n\n## MXC CEO Sheen Hu talks on Smart City\nOn Tuesday CEO Sheen Hu made his way to Brussels where he spoke with the EU about digital innovation in Smart Cities. A primary topic was regulation in Smart Cities. Sheen was quick to speak up for regulation, stating that regulation is the key to bringing order to a chaotic market.\n\n## Jeff spreads messages on blockchain in mobility and logistics\nAlso on Tuesday Jeff joined the Berlin Partner for Business and Technology and SIBB, the digital business association for Berlin Brandenburg to discuss Blockchain Transformation in Mobility and Logistics. During the event, Jeff presented the MXC solution for Decentralized Wireless as a way to break free from high-cost networks for smart cities and industrial connectivity. The message was well-received, and lead to a number of promising conversations, including one that could launch MXC to space.\n\n## MXC to present at Smart City Expo Barcelona\nFollowing Tuesday’s event, Jeff visited Berlin Partner’s office on Wednesday to discuss MXC’s involvement at the Smart City Expo World Congress in Barcelona. Both Jeff and Aaron will be in Barcelona November 19 to 21, exhibiting MXC as the foundation for wireless connectivity in smart cities. Send an email to [hello@mxc.org](mailto:hello@mxc.org) if you would like to meet with them there. \n\n## Another successful Meet Up in Amsterdam\nLast Friday the MXC Community Team traveled to Amsterdam to host our second annual meetup for the lively community there. It was a widely successful event, bringing both community veterans and MXC newbies together to discuss what we’ve accomplished over the past year, and to discover what’s coming up next for MXC. \n\n## Upcoming events in South Korea\nMXC is headed to South Korea! MXC-1 (Siwon) will join the Korean Government to discuss the need for a reliable wireless network in smart cities during the Smart City Expo in Seoul on October 1st. Leading up to the event he’ll also attend the Blockfesta on September 27, host a meetup on September 28, and attending various events from September 29 to October 2 during the Korea Blockchain Week. \n\nThis has been this week’s news update. I look forward to speaking with all of you again next week. Until then, get active, get in the community, ask us questions — because it’s only together that we can build the Future of IoT.","date":"September 16, 2019","metaDescription":"Sheen is back from EIT Digital Conference in Brussels. MXC hosted its annual Amsterdam meet up, and you can meet MXC in Seoul and Barcelona.","video":"Sheen is back from EIT Digital Conference in Brussels. MXC hosted its annual Amsterdam meet up, and you can meet MXC in Seoul and Barcelona.","slug":"mxc-in-brussels-amsterdam-seoul-and-barcelona"},"tags":[{"tag":"MXC News Update","slug":"mxc-news-update"}],"author":{"author":"Siwon Kim","slug":"siwon-kim"},"zhch_post":{"post":{"slug":"布鲁塞尔，阿姆斯特丹，首尔和巴塞罗那的mxc极域"}},"zhtw_post":{"post":{"slug":"布魯塞爾，阿姆斯特丹，首爾和巴塞羅那的mxc極域社群"}},"ko_post":null},"hans":{"category":{"zhchCategory":"新闻更新","zhchSlug":"新闻更新"},"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='225'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20225'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M0%207l1%208v1L0%2031v15l5-6c6-6%2010-11%2010-13l1-1c0%202%200%202%202%201v-3c-2%201-3-2-2-3v-2l4%202c1%201%201%201%205-2%203-4%203-4%201-5l-2-1h2l6-2-5-2c-5-1-8-3-5-3l6%202c5%201%205%201%207-1l2-5V0H0v7m55-6c-3%209-4%2014-3%2014l3%201c1%201%201%201-2%201h-3l4%201h3l-5%201-4%202-1%206c-3%206-2%206%202%204l5-2c3%200%201%202-4%204l-5%202%202%205c9-4%208-1-4%207a672%20672%200%2000-17%2045l7%204%203-4c4-5%205-4%202%201l-3%205%203%202%201%201c-6-1-6-1-8%203l-2%204%206%203c9%204%208%205%200%202l-7-2-2%202-6%209-4%205%209-16v-2h-2l-1-1h-2l-1%204-3%208-2%205c-2%202-1%200%201-8%204-10%204-10-3-13-8-3-7-4%201-1l6%202c2-2%204-12%203-13L9%2082l4%202%207%204%204%203%203-9a262%20262%200%20008-30l-3%202-4%202-14%208%208-7%2011-6%201-1c0-1-13%205-19%2010-5%203-6%204-6%202l4-4c7-4%2013-10%2012-11v-2l5-3%208-5%203-2-6-3-6-3A249%20249%200%20007%2061l-3%204-2%202c-1%202-1%202%201%202%203-1%203%200%200%202-4%202-4%2024-1%2027%201%201%202%202%201%203l3%2018c3%2017%203%2017%204%2015l